Target: Church Selector - Walla Walla


THE PATH TO GROWING YOUR CHURCH
================================

✦ COMMUNICATE EFFICIENTLY
  • Reach your entire congregation instantly
  • Consistent messaging across all channels
  • Less admin work, more ministry time
  • Mobile ready - web, notifications, and text messages

✦ CREATE MORE SERVICES FOR SPIRITUAL GROWTH
  • Online devotionals and Bible studies
  • Sermon archives for deeper reflection
  • Prayer request systems
  • Small group coordination

✦ MAXIMIZE YOUR FACILITIES
  • Utilize church infrastructure during non-worship days
  • Promote community programs:
    - Life skills workshops
    - Home services ministry
    - Free laundry days
    - Food drives
    - Cooking classes
    - Computer & tech classes
  • Event registration and sign-ups
  • Volunteer scheduling for each program

✦ INCREASE GIVING THROUGH ENGAGEMENT
  • Higher attendance = higher giving
  • Easy recurring donations (subscription-based)
  • Transparent stewardship reporting
  • Special campaign support

✦ EMPOWER MEMBERS TO INVITE
  • One-click sermon sharing
  • Digital invite cards from the pastor
  • Event pages designed for social sharing
  • First-time visitor welcome flow

✦ BUILD A STRONGER COMMUNITY
  • Member & officer directories that connect
  • Volunteer coordination tools
  • Celebration of milestones (baptisms, anniversaries)
  • Youth and children's ministry pages

✦ EXTEND YOUR REACH BEYOND SUNDAY
  • Livestream integration
  • Midweek devotional emails
  • Mobile access anywhere, anytime
  • Global mission updates


HOW YOUR WEBSITE BUILDS COMMUNITY
=================================

Your website isn't just information—it's a community-building tool.

SHARED PURPOSE & IDENTITY
  → Mission/Vision/Values pages unite your congregation
  → Consistent branding reinforces who you are

CONSISTENT COMMUNICATION
  → Weekly newsletters keep everyone connected
  → Text notifications for timely updates
  → Two-way contact forms for dialogue

MEANINGFUL CONNECTION
  → Small group directories help people find their tribe
  → Member profiles foster relationships
  → Intergenerational ministry pages

ACTIVE PARTICIPATION
  → Volunteer sign-up forms
  → Ministry team pages with clear roles
  → Event registration that's easy

CELEBRATION & RECOGNITION
  → Milestone announcements (baptisms, anniversaries)
  → Photo galleries of church life
  → Member spotlight features

CARE & SUPPORT
  → Prayer request submissions
  → Care ministry information
  → Crisis response contacts

WELCOMING NEWCOMERS
  → "I'm New" page with clear next steps
  → First-time visitor flow
  → Connection card integration

SHARED EXPERIENCES
  → Event pages with photos and stories
  → Retreat and fellowship promotion
  → Memory-making through shared content

SERVANT LEADERSHIP
  → Pastor's messages and updates
  → Leadership transparency
  → Accessible contact information

OUTWARD FOCUS
  → Community service program pages
  → Mission trip updates
  → Local impact stories


