YOUR DEDICATED WEBMASTER
========================
We become your website editor-in-chief. Our duties include:
• Updating your website content
• Adding new sermons
• Adding new events
• Adding new newsletters
• Updating About Us, Mission, Vision, Values, History
• Any changes you need

HOW IT WORKS
------------
No complicated WordPress commands!
Simply send us your content in Microsoft Word or Google Docs
and we'll place it on the website for you.

→ You focus on ministry. We handle the tech.


